If you're have any doubts about mentioning Bitcoin to your listeners, there is no need to go into detail - not do you need to mention it at all. No Bitcoin experience is required to start supporting you on Fountain. The most important thing is that they understand that they are sending you value in return for the value you are providing them.

As we have explained, a podcasters motive to ask their audience to support them is more than just so that they can get paid. Supporting on Fountain can also be "sold in" to your audience purely on the basis that it will help bring more listeners in and give your community a place to hang out together. Try and think about it from their perspective and understand how it will benefit them - not just you.

